{
 "name": "RPlog_One_Bad_Day",
 "title": "One Bad Day",
 "summary": "Hunted across Plaxton City, the dark-side adept Simon Sezirok is cornered in Fountain Square by the proud Rodian bounty hunter Detjin, whose modified scout armor and elitist hunter's air mark him as a relentless pursuer. After Simon's separated companion Mira goes missing, the two clash in a brutal alley duel of lightstaff against grappling cable and blaster, Simon binding Detjin with the Force while Detjin tries to reel him in, until Simon carves an escape through the floor as Caspian marines close in. Later, on Hideaway Beach, a battered Simon is found by the Jedi student Ethan Katana and NRI Captain James K'Cusi, who has been shadowing them. Old tension flares between Simon and the Jedi, but the meeting turns to grim news: Markus and Mira have been abducted by a woman calling herself Kacela Ulara, and the search for them is underway.",
